question: Koh-choán kiāⁿ-chiàⁿ hō͘-chòe (β) chòe kiông-kái ê thong-kè chèng-kè, iû siāng koân ê tòe-ài-tiám (absolute t-value) lâi piáu-chāi?
Tī p < 0.05 ê sî-hāu，sû-kì-bú-ha̍k-siōng ū-hāu-ît ê só͘-ū alpha (α) hē-sè-jī ê pêng-kin phó͘-chún-liâu sī tah-iūⁿ?
Tī sián-suànn ê hāng-bo̍k (iōng ē-á-siòng ê sò͘-ba̍k lâi piáu-sī) lāi-bīn, ê-tàng β coefficient iú siōng khoah ê 95% sìn-jīn tio̍h-khuànn, hō-sò͘ ūi-tio̍h ê α coefficient ê p-jiáh sī siáⁿ-mih?
Chiu iōng β hōe-sò͘ ê tōa-hūn chhin-chhiūⁿ, chiū-chāi tùi 1 kàu 6 ê sî, ū chi̍t-ê tiāu-kiāⁿ ê phòe-tūi bô? Ū chi̍t-ê chèng-chóng ê hêng-thài bô?
answer: Bô chi̍t-ê chèng-chóng ê tōa-hūn phòe-tūi. Tāi-seng ê β hōe-sò͘ tùi β₁ (0.7208) kàu β₂ (0.8237) chin-chiok, tān-sī āu-lâi tùi β₃ (0.0025) kap āu-lâi ê bô-hêng kái-chè chin tōa. Chi̍t-ê ê siúⁿ nn̄g ê chi̍t-pō͘-hūn ê tōa-hūn pí tē-saⁿ kàu tē-la̍k ê chi̍t-pō͘-hūn chin tōa, in lóng chin kūn 0.

question: Tōa-sè tōa-sè ê kiūⁿ-chiáⁿ (α) hō͘-sòan sī siau-sit bô-tiāⁿ-it-ê (P-tiâⁿ > 0.4) chiàⁿ-chhiúⁿ, i-ê hū-sòan phín-chha̍t (standard error) koh-chài sió-kóa 0.03, chiah ē-tàng lia̍h-chún chē-chē kiūⁿ-chiáⁿ?
Sáⁿ-chiok-tang kó͘-chiáⁿ ê hō͘-chiáⁿ (α kah β lóng-chóng) sī chin chē ê kai-tú (p-ài lú 0.05 ê), kóa-chiáh phah-suànn ê tit-tio̍h?

Nāi-bán chiah-ūi α₁ êModel êStandard Error siâⁿ-chē kǹg, i ê t-statistic tit-tit-tâi sī-chóan-chi̍t? Ké-kò͘ tâi-siōng ê chiah-ūi Model ê t-statistic kap p-value chi-kan ê koan-hē lâi-kó͘, i ê α₁ coefficient tiāⁿ-tit-tâi chiap-chhiok tio̍h kó͘-séng-bē (p < 0.05)?
answer: Tâi-tit-tâi ê t-statistic chiâⁿ-chò -1.593 (-0.0215 / (0.027 / 2)). Chiah-ê kái-piàn chin bô-khó-lêng kā coefficient chiap-chhiok tio̍h kó͘-séng. Chhı̄-châi α₂ Model ê t-statistic sī -2.803 kap p-value sī 0.005. Chiah-ê t-statistic ê sió-tiō-á ê t-giâⁿ-tâi chhin-chhiūⁿ -1.593 ê p-value koh-khah-kō, siáⁿ-khó-lêng iáu sī chhiau-kòe 0.05 ê kó͘-séng tiâu-kiāⁿ, chiâⁿ-chòe tīng-gī ê t-value it-poaⁿ ài tāi-iok 2 tòe í-siōng.

question: Giam-giām β hō-sò͘ ê tōa-sè kah i tùi-èng ê t-thiau-liōng ū siáⁿ-mih koan-hē. Hō-sò͘ ke-tōa mā ē-tàng chhōa-tó͘ tōa ê t-thiau-liōng bē?
answer: Bōe, β hō-sò͘ ke-tōa bô it-tēng ē chhōa-tó͘ tōa ê t-thiau-liōng. Chhiūⁿ-chā, β₂ ū siōng tōa ê hō-sò͘ (0.8237) tān-sī i ê t-thiau-liōng (8.418) khah-chē khah-sè kā β₄ (126.061) koh-iā-ū, in-ūi β₄ ê hō-sò͘ khah-sè (0.0041). T-thiau-liōng sī hō-sò͘ kah i ê piau-chún-chhò-cha (standard error) ê pí-luât, só͘-í chiâⁿ-chē sè ê piau-chún-chhò-cha ē-tàng chhōa-tó͘ chiâⁿ-chē tōa ê t-thiau-liōng tōa-chhéng sī sé-sé ê hō-sò͘, chhin-chhiūⁿ 0n β₃ kàu β₆ ê chêng-hêng.

question: Siaⁿ-kè ê sêng-hun tiong, ū-ê tiāⁿ-chè 95% sìn-liâm tiāⁿ-kan bô pau-koah 0, ē-tàng tòe bî-chih 0.05 ê P-tiāⁿ-taⁿ. Chit-ê phiau (table) lāi-bīn ū ūi-ê sêng-hun ê sìn-liâm tiāⁿ-kan kap P-tiāⁿ-taⁿ bô kāng chi̍t-ê chha-jit, m̄-koh ē-tàng chiap-sū chiah-ê su-siok bô?
answer: Bô, chit-ê phiau lāi-bīn ê sêng-hun lóng sī hō͘-siong siong-tông ê, tùi in ê P-tiāⁿ-taⁿ kap 95% sìn-liâm tiāⁿ-kan. Koh-ū sêng-hun ê P-tiāⁿ-taⁿ lóng bī-chih 0.05 (chhin-chhiūⁿ β₁, α₂, β₂) ūi-ê sìn-liâm tiāⁿ-kan bô pau-koah 0. Tòe-chiah, koh-ū sêng-hun ê P-tiāⁿ-taⁿ lóng koh-khah-kē 0.05 (chhin-chhiūⁿ α₁, α₃, α₄) ūi-ê sìn-liâm tiāⁿ-kan sī pau-koah 0 ê.

question: Na-ti alpha (α) coefficient ê t-statistic si siánn-ê si-kúi siânn toā-ê chhut-miâ tōa-ê ke-á (outlier) tang-tiong kah pa̍t-ê alpha coefficient ê t-statistic pí?
answer: α₆, i ê t-statistic sī 7.305, sī siâⁿ toā ê chhut-miâ toā-ê ke-á (outlier). Pa̍t-ê alpha t-statistic sī -0.787, -2.803, -0.269, 0.013, kah 0.729. Chē-chē ê chia ê sò͘-jī lóng chha-put-toan tī -3 kah 1 ê tiong-kan. 7.305 ê kóa-ta̍t chin-chiok toā-ê la̍r-tōa, koh sī siâⁿ-chi̍t-ê toā-ê chiàⁿ-sò͘-jī, hō͘ i kah pa̍t-ê hō͘-siong tùi-chhiat.
